import ACCOUNT from './account.svg'
import FILE_CONTRACT from './file-contract.svg'
import ARROW_RIGHT from './arrow-right.svg'

import { ReactComponent as ACCOUNT_SVG } from './account.svg'
import { ReactComponent as FILE_CONTRACT_SVG } from './file-contract.svg'
import { ReactComponent as ARROW_RIGHT_SVG } from './arrow-right.svg'

export const Icons = {
  Account: ACCOUNT,
  FileContract: FILE_CONTRACT,
  ArrowRight: ARROW_RIGHT,
}

export const IconsSvg = {
  Account: ACCOUNT_SVG,
  FileContract: FILE_CONTRACT_SVG,
  ArrowRight: ARROW_RIGHT_SVG,
}
